TITLE: Defining Inline Content Types in TypeScript for BlockNote
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines TypeScript types for inline content in BlockNote, including Link and StyledText. It demonstrates how rich text content is structured within blocks, including styling and link properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/typecellos/blocknote/blob/main/docs/pages/docs/editor-basics/document-structure.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
type Link = {
  type: "link";
  content: StyledText[];
  href: string;
};

type StyledText = {
  type: "text";
  text: string;
  styles: Styles;
};

type InlineContent = Link | StyledText;
```

