TITLE: Implementing Editable Custom Inline Content in BlockNote
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create editable custom inline content using the vanilla JS API. It shows the implementation of a 'mention' type that can be edited, including handling content updates and triggering UI interactions.
